<LocalizedProperties><Language>en</Language><Title>Security Update for Office XP (KB920821)</Title><Description>Microsoft has released an update for Microsoft Office XP. A security vulnerability exists in Office XP programs that could allow arbitrary code to run when you open a maliciously modified file. This update resolves that vulnerability.</Description><MoreInfoUrl>http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?FamilyId=B26ADC3C-1DB8-46FD-8381-B199EE351E7C&amp;displaylang=en</MoreInfoUrl><SupportUrl>http://support.microsoft.com/oas/default.aspx?LN=en-us&amp;gprid=6527&amp;x=9&amp;y=8</SupportUrl></LocalizedProperties>